NAME
	caught_error - get information on the last caught error

SYNOPSIS
	string caught_error(varargs mixed arg)

DESCRIPTION
	Get information about the last caught error.  If flag contains
	something, the entire error trace is returned, otherwise only
	the error itself is returned.

RETURN VALUE
	Returns a string with information if an error was caught, nil
	otherwise.

EXAMPLES
	if (caught_error()) {
	   this_player()->tell(caught_error(1));
	}

SEE ALSO
	afun/catch, afun/rethrow
